{"tid":1691183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如一齊去港灣消防局聲援手足?","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T16:04:11.000Z","uid":326824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51c8f5699976010724be233a4aef0490264a198a","tid":1691183,"uid":326824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"消防手足俾狗圍單野, 班消防膠層出埋篇咁撚樣的聲明, 話咩一場誤會, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">擺明同班前線消防兄弟割𥱊</span>, 含黑警曱甴含到雪雪聲, 我屌你老母消防高層冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家果位挺直腰板做人的阿sir唔單止俾狗圍俾狗屌, 俾高層照肺, 晉升前途盡毀之餘, 仲俾藍絲曱甴起底欺凌, 你班連登仔如果唔出聲, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係咪想當消防手足係condom?</span> 我屌埋你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家記唔記得, 金鐘海富爆閘事件, 消防手足救返幾多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又記唔記得, 每次發夢ge前線好街坊好, 一俾狗扑到頭破血流要入廠, 全靠同屬消防處的救護員專業救治<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有消防手足報夢俾我知, 呢兩日好多平時敢言的三柴俾班消防白衫照肺, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫佢地唔好搞事</span>。 依家好多消防rank and file都憤憤不平, 有堆三柴手足覺得反正都升到盡, 不如逼工會宮, 要脅消防管方企硬, 否則要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">另組消防手足工會, 爭取更大保障!</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟不才, 但覺得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地市民都要做返D野</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢, 俾狗搞果位消防sir就守<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">灣仔港灣局</span> (即係稅局隔離呀, 黨鐵A5出口過橋), 不如我地整下文宣呀, 貼memo紙呀, 買d顏色鮮豔ge花送去呀, 務求令到消防高層見到, 令全世界見到, 我地香港人 #StandWithFiremen , 同前線消防員救護員齊上齊落, 大家點睇? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n解散警隊曱甴 清算刻不容緩<br />\n香港人 反抗!"},{"pid":"34a1292cfda5f2cd225754a90f900f0a372e3df3","tid":1691183,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:25:32.000Z","msg":"［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0c0501944aa899cc88882e18ec556c79126d6ddc","tid":1691183,"uid":326824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:30:09.000Z","msg":"P牌無力自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47eb08270c0f0d4ca2f7e49e4c45cd59a28e66a","tid":1691183,"uid":105298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"立場話佢被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b62f8c55594bc9d09d9acc4fd37428356225b6","tid":1691183,"uid":190396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"［最新戰術討論］拉一派打一派，分化敵人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689534</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1ed8bf9e84992b41120e075e5831606ff1195b41","tid":1691183,"uid":239510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">低調啦 寫信去撐 <br />\n有時發大來搞當時人俾人針對得更慘</span>"},{"pid":"58454a37ac64e5b3e618014261799261a7e9156d","tid":1691183,"uid":114364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"幾點 ！"},{"pid":"af137a9b2d70de3aec95130b4b04a20e0f0b229d","tid":1691183,"uid":326824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"寫信去的話等於俾高層石沉大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實個手足都通曬天, 係時候展現民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗約定時間, 大家各自去貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3babf72c2d58681f767850dd717694b82a6d74","tid":1691183,"uid":326824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"P仔無力自推2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}